Starscream

Starscream yelped in pain as Inferno jammed him. But this gave him 
the opportunity. He knew Inferno was in the exactly the right spot to 
give him the shock of his life. Starscream used all his force to move 
upward. Slowly and horitantly, as to not shake any things off his 
body. As they got to a tremendous height, Starscream blew out all his 
exhaust and grime that were in his jets into Inferno's face, hoping 
to knock him off and to send him plummiting to the earth.
